{
  "lifecycles": [
    {
      "id": "networking-gslb-service",
      "service": "networking/gslb",
      "enabled": true,
      "heavy": false,
      "_note": "GSLB CRUD (Wave 2, NOT runtime-proven). GSLB is a global/account-scoped, VPC-free resource, so no shared-VPC adoption. Create -> get -> set -> set-health-check -> set-resources -> set-routing-control -> delete, all in one optional 'gslb' group so a bad body skips only this family (cleaned up). Bodies from data/api_docs.json request_example. create returns $.gslb.id (from creategslb response_example {gslb:{...,health_check:{id:...}}} — the top-level gslb.id is the resource id, health_check.id is a sub-id). Captured SOFT into gslb_id; dependent steps reference {gslb_id} (real chain on success; literal-but-norm-matching on 4xx -> still records coverage). Enum guesses (UNVALIDATED): algorithm=ROUND_ROBIN, env_usage=PUBLIC, name must be an FQDN -> regr{ualpha}.gslb.e.samsungsdscloud.com. health_check/resources sub-objects sent mostly empty per docs example (empty strings); set-resources requires resources:[{description,destination,region,weight}]; set-routing-control requires {region,status:ENABLE}. region filled with {region}. Covers all 6 GSLB WRITE ops: POST /v1/gslbs, PUT /v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}, PUT /v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}/health-check, PUT /v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}/resources, PUT /v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}/routing-control, DELETE /v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}.",
      "steps": [
        {
          "name": "create-gslb",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/gslbs",
          "group": "gslb",
          "optional": true,
          "json": {
            "algorithm": "ROUND_ROBIN",
            "description": "API regression suite",
            "env_usage": "PUBLIC",
            "health_check": {
              "health_check_interval": "",
              "health_check_probe_timeout": "",
              "health_check_user_id": "",
              "health_check_user_password": "",
              "protocol": "",
              "receive_string": "",
              "send_string": "",
              "service_port": "",
              "timeout": ""
            },
            "name": "regr{ualpha}.gslb.e.samsungsdscloud.com",
            "resources": [],
            "tags": []
          },
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202, 400, 403, 404, 409, 422],
          "capture_soft": {"gslb_id": "$.gslb.id"},
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}",
            "service": "gslb"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "get-gslb",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}",
          "group": "gslb",
          "optional": true,
          "expect_status": [200, 400, 403, 404]
        },
        {
          "name": "set-gslb",
          "method": "PUT",
          "path": "/v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}",
          "group": "gslb",
          "optional": true,
          "json": {
            "algorithm": "ROUND_ROBIN",
            "description": "API regression suite (updated)"
          },
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202, 400, 403, 404, 409, 422]
        },
        {
          "name": "set-gslb-health-check",
          "method": "PUT",
          "path": "/v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}/health-check",
          "group": "gslb",
          "optional": true,
          "json": {
            "health_check_interval": "",
            "health_check_probe_timeout": "",
            "health_check_user_id": "",
            "health_check_user_password": "",
            "protocol": "",
            "receive_string": "",
            "send_string": "",
            "service_port": "",
            "timeout": ""
          },
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202, 400, 403, 404, 409, 422]
        },
        {
          "name": "set-gslb-resources",
          "method": "PUT",
          "path": "/v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}/resources",
          "group": "gslb",
          "optional": true,
          "json": {
            "resources": [
              {
                "description": "API regression suite",
                "destination": "192.0.2.10",
                "region": "{region}",
                "weight": 0
              }
            ]
          },
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202, 400, 403, 404, 409, 422]
        },
        {
          "name": "set-gslb-routing-control",
          "method": "PUT",
          "path": "/v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}/routing-control",
          "group": "gslb",
          "optional": true,
          "json": {
            "region": "{region}",
            "status": "ENABLE"
          },
          "expect_status": [200, 201, 202, 400, 403, 404, 409, 422]
        },
        {
          "name": "probe-gslb-reads",
          "probe_reads": {"gslb_id": "{gslb_id}"}
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-gslb",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/gslbs/{gslb_id}",
          "group": "gslb",
          "optional": true,
          "destructive": true,
          "expect_status": [200, 202, 204, 400, 403, 404, 409]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
